Author: slohiya
Topic: Does the platform offer licensing flexibility?
Body: The MSP cloud management platform introduces flexible licensing, details of which can be found in the Admin Guide under the 'Licensing' section. This flexibility enables MSPs to deliver differentiated services to their customers.
